      "frameId": "f-0",
      "visualKind": "card",
      "title": "<p>US 1146 — Enable Google Account Login</p>",
      "body": "<p><strong>User Story:</strong> </p><p>As a first-time user, I want to sign up for the product using my Google account, so that I can start using the core features immediately without creating a new password.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Acceptance Criteria:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\"></span>The user is presented with a &#34;Sign in with Google&#34; button on the login screen.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\"></span>Selecting the button successfully creates an account and logs the user in on the first attempt.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\"></span>The system automatically pulls the user&#39;s name and email from the Google profile.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\"></span>The user is directed to the main product dashboard upon successful login.</li></ol>"
    },
